                    <a id="downloadPDFLink" class="inline-block bg-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-purple-800 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-800 tooltip" style="display: none;" role="button" data-tooltip="Download the combined PDF" aria-label="Download PDF">Download PDF</a>
